    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add <strong>half</strong> the <strong>soy sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!) to the <strong>browned pork mince </strong>and the <strong>sliced green beans</strong> and cook for 4 min further or until the pork is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>soy pork & green beans</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
