    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>Sichuan-style chilli sauce</strong> to the bottom of your serving bowls</p><p>Serve the <strong>drained noodles</strong> on top with the <strong>soy pork & green beans</strong> and <strong>grated carrot</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>To eat, toss the noodles and veg through the Sichuan-style chilli sauce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
